<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>search on Mathis Gauthey's Website</title><link>https://mathisgauthey.github.io/mathisgauthey.github.io_old/tags/search/</link><description>Recent content in search on Mathis Gauthey's Website</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 07 Nov 2022 11:09:05 +0100</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://mathisgauthey.github.io/mathisgauthey.github.io_old/tags/search/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to Search Efficiently Online</title><link>https://mathisgauthey.github.io/mathisgauthey.github.io_old/how-to-search-efficiently-online/</link><pubDate>Mon, 07 Nov 2022 11:09:05 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://mathisgauthey.github.io/mathisgauthey.github.io_old/how-to-search-efficiently-online/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="how-to-search-efficiently-online">How to Search Efficiently Online&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="exclude-à-term-from-your-search">Exclude À Term From Your Search&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Add a &lt;code>-&lt;/code> before the word to exclude.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">dolfins -footbal
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>You&amp;rsquo;ll get animals, not a footbal team.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="if-you-want-synonyms-in-the-result">If You Want Synonyms in the Result&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Add a &lt;code>~&lt;/code> before the word if you want synonyms.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">music ~classes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Here you&amp;rsquo;ll get music classes, lessons, coaching, etc.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="search-within-a-specific-website">Search Within a Specific Website&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to search inside a specific website → &lt;code>site:&lt;/code>reddit.com&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">How to do that site:reddit.com
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="or-and-">Or and |&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to use &lt;strong>OR&lt;/strong> while searching ? → &lt;code>OR&lt;/code> or &lt;code>|&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Netflix | Prime &amp;lt;=&amp;gt; Netflix OR Prime
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="search-within-two-number-ranges">Search Within Two Number Ranges&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to search within a range ? → &lt;code>1914..1918&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Movies 1980..2000
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="find-news-related-to-a-particular-location">Find News Related to a Particular Location&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to search inside a specific location only ? → &lt;code>location:&lt;/code>France&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Weather alert location:france
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="filter-by-file-type">Filter by File Type&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to search for a specific filetype ? → &lt;code>filetype:&lt;/code>pdf&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Bible filetype:pdf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="search-exactly-for-that-word">Search Exactly for That Word&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to search exactly for a word ? → &lt;code>&amp;quot;word&amp;quot;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;#34;Jean Claude&amp;#34; le chauffagiste
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Gives you the results with the full name, not just the first or last one.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="eliminate-sites-that-flood-the-results">Eliminate Sites That Flood the Results&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Comment retirer un site qui donne des résultats de merde ? → &lt;code>-site:&lt;/code>pinterest.*&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">-site:pinterest.*
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>